<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8030410>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Hemidactylus paucifasciatus sp. nov. (holotype, ZSI-R-28357): (A) dorsal view of body, (B) ventral view of body. Scale bars 10 mm, photos by Akshay Khandekar." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8030410/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8030416>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Detailed pholidosis at mid-body of Hemidactylus paucifasciatus sp. nov. (holotype, ZSI-R-28357): (A) dorsal side and (B) ventral side. Scale bars 10 mm, photos by Akshay Khandekar." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8030416/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8030412>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Hemidactylus paucifasciatus sp. nov. (holotype, ZSI-R-28357): (A) dorsal view of head, (B) ventral view of head, (C) lateral view of head, (D) view of femoral region showing femoral pores, (E) ventral view of right manus, and (F) ventral view of right pes. Scale bars 5 mm, photos by Akshay Khandekar." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8030412/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8030420>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Hemidactylus paucifasciatus sp. nov. in life: (A) male, holotype, ZSI-R-28357 (B) male, paratype, NCBS-BH668 and (C) sub-adult female, paratype, ZSI-CZRC-7117. Photos by Rakesh Kumar Mohalik (A, C) and Pratyush P. Mohapatra (B)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8030420/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8030422>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Paratypes of Hemidactylus paucifasciatus sp. nov., from left to right, ZSI-CZRC-7117 NCBS-BH668 NCBS- BH669. Scale bars 10 mm, photo by Akshay Khandekar." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8030422/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8030406>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. (A) Relief map of Odisha and neighbouring states showing the distribution of members of the sushilduttai and triedrus clades, and (B) Maximum Likelihood phylogeny of the prashadi group of Indian Hemidactylus based on the protein coding ND2 gene. Bootstrap support shown and nodes and major clades marked." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8030406/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8030426>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Habitat photo of Hemidactylus paucifasciatus sp. nov. from Gadachandi Temple, Anandapur, Kendujhar District, Odisha State, India. Photo Pratyush P. Mohapatra." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8030426/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

